snippet.title: Flintlock: The Siege of Dawn | Story Trailer
snippet.description:
"Dawn burned. And the Gods ran awry."

Prepare to confront the relentless fury of the Gods in Flintlock: The Siege of Dawn. Take a first look at the Gods, and learn about their motivations in our latest trailer.

Secure your pre-order now and gear up to reclaim the City of Dawn: https://www.playflintlock.com/linkhub

Out July 18th.
